# FILE: halabFreelance/freelancePublicProfile/freelancePublicProfile.desc
# ROLE: Talent Showcase & Professional Identity Card
# ROUTE: /freelance/profile/:id
# ACCOUNT: All types can view — only freelancers have this page
# THEME: Dark · modern portfolio · trust signals

## 1. IDENTITY HEADER (Top Fold)
- AVATAR: large rounded-full · gradient-bg placeholder or user photo
  - GLOW: shadow-[#6366F1]/30 if isVerified === true (student) or business account (auto-verified)
- FREELANCER TYPE BADGE:
  - "مستقل طلابي" — indigo bg/border · shown for Student accounts (isFreelancer: true)
  - "مستقل خارجي" — amber bg/border · shown for businessType === 'freelancer'
- VERIFIED BADGE: [✅ موثّق] if student is verified by admin
- NAME: text-2xl font-bold text-[#F1F5F9]
- TITLE: "مطوّر Full-Stack (MERN)"
- BIO: short punchline in italics · muted
- STATS BAR: ⭐ Rating · 💼 Projects · ⚡ Response Time · 🎓 Level (for students)

## 2. SKILLS & TOOLS BENTO
- TECH TAGS: flex-wrap · rounded-full pills · bg-[#6366F1]/10 · border-[#6366F1]/20
  - [ React.js ] [ Node.js ] [ MongoDB ] [ Tailwind ] [ Linux ]
- CERTS: links to completed Academy course certificates

## 3. WORK PORTFOLIO
- GRID: grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 · rounded-2xl cards
- Each item: screenshot thumbnail → click → lightbox
  - LIGHTBOX: image + challenge description + client review quote

## 4. SERVICE CATALOG (What I Offer)
- Small service cards: title + fixed price + delivery time
- ACTION: [💳 اطلب الخدمة] → contract/project request form

## 5. HIRE ME TERMINAL (Sticky Sidebar)
- STATUS: [🟢 متاح للعمل] | [🟡 مشغول]
- PRIMARY CTA: [💬 تواصل للعمل] — opens project proposal form
- ESCROW NOTE: "المدفوعات محمية عبر نظام الضمان في HalabUnver"

## 6. RATINGS & REVIEWS
- Chronological list · ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ + review text + anonymous user
- Average rating displayed prominently in identity header

## 7. ADMIN OVERLAY
- accountType === 'admin': floating [🧊 تجميد] [✅ إلغاء التجميد] buttons
